The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | International | Bangla lashes
                                                                                                               Bangla lashes
                            
	Dhaka, June 29 (PTI): A 40-year-old widow was whipped 202 times along with a man for her alleged involvement in anti-social activities in southeastern Bangladesh.        
	Piara Begum, a mother of five, was whipped 202 times while 25-year-old Mamun Miah received 101 lashes in Comilla on Saturday. The woman, who fell unconscious after the lashings, was admitted to a local hospital.                                                                                                                                                                                     
